INTRODUCTION
This Document is the Work Instruction (WI) for Management Reviews
PURPOSE
This WI defines the steps that are followed to implement and monitor Management
Reviews in the organisation
SCOPE
The WI applies to the QMSrs Tool set that accompanies this WI

MANAGEMENT REVIEWS WORK INSTRUCTION
MANAGEMENT REVIEWS PROCESS
This section displays the flow of the process.
MANAGEMENT REVIEW SETTINGS
In this section the user can add, edit and delete the action type and review category
Action Type
In this section the user can add, edit and delete the action type
ADD AN ACTION TYPE
 Go to Management Reviews section in the QMS.
 From Management Review Settings select ‘Action Type’.
 Click on create icon " “.
 Enter the title of the action type and its description.
 Click on “Save “to save the amended data or “Cancel” to cancel the changes.

EDIT AN ACTION TYPE
 Go to Management Reviews section in the QMS.
 From Management Review Settings select ‘Action Type’.
 Click on edit icon“ “beside the type that you want to edit.
 Make the necessary changes.
 Click on “Save “to save the amended data or “Cancel” to cancel the changes.
DELETE AN ACTION TYPE
 Go to Management Reviews section in the QMS.
 From Management Review Settings select ‘Action Type’.
 Click on delete icon “ “beside the type that you want to delete.
 To delete the Type click on “OK “or “Cancel “to cancel deleting.

MANAGEMENT REVIEW SCHEDUALE
This section displays the management reviews schedule with their status.
Click on management review title to view management review details (ID and title)
User can edit a review (if the review is not completed or cancelled) or delete it.
EDIT A REVIEW
 Go to Management Reviews section in the QMS.
 Select ‘Management Review Schedule’.
 Click on the title of the review that you want to edit.
 Click on edit icon“ “that appears at the end of the window.
 Make the necessary changes.
 Click on “Save “to save the amended data or “Cancel” to cancel the changes.

CREATE NEW REVIEW
This section explains how to create a review in the QMS.
To create a review:
 Go to Management Reviews section in the QMS.
 Select ‘Create New Review’.
 Fill the mandatory fields with the red asterisk ‘*’ and any other fields you
have data for.
 Click on save icon “ ” to save changes that appears at the top of the
window.

SEARCH A TASK
 Go to Management Reviews section in the QMS
 Select ‘Manage Tasks’.
 Click on filter icon “ “at the top of the window, then select the search
criteria.
 Fill the text field or select from the drop down list which depends on the
search criteria you choose.

REPORTS
MANAGEMENT REVIEWS LIST
This section displays all the Management Reviews in the system with the RAG status
(Red-Amber-Green) for priorities.
Different filter criteria can be used (Representative, Organization unit, Review
Status, Record Mode …).
You can use varying criteria as follows:
 Click on filter icon “ “at the top of the window, then choose the search
criteria you want.
 Select from the drop down list and click on next icon" ".
 To clear the result of filtration click on delete Filter icon" ".
In this dynamic report, the user can choose the fields that he wants to appear in the
table by selecting from the drop down list of “display fields” that found at the top of
the page and then click on “ “ icon.
ANNUAL REVIEW TASK STATUS
In this section user can display all the review task actions with their status.
User can select the year from the drop down list.
